</p>
<p>
    <strong>3. Are there brook trout in the Willamette River?</strong><br>
    No, brook trout prefer colder, higher elevation lakes and streams. They’re rare in major rivers like the Willamette.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>4. Do I need a fishing license to fish near Portland?</strong><br>
    Yes, anyone age 12 or older must have a valid Oregon fishing license.
